          "Now add the two leftover principal arctangents $\\tan^{-1}(-\\tfrac47)+\\tan^{-1}(-\\tfrac{3}{11})$. Their product is $(-\\tfrac47)(-\\tfrac{3}{11})=\\tfrac{12}{77}<1$, so no further correction; the combined tangent is $\\frac{-\\frac47-\\frac{3}{11}}{1-\\frac{12}{77}}=\\frac{-65/77}{65/77}=-1$, giving $\\tan^{-1}(-1)=-\\tfrac{\\pi}{4}$.",
          "Therefore the total is $\\bigl(-\\tfrac{\\pi}{4}\\bigr)+2\\pi=\\dfrac{7\\pi}{4}$, matching the staircase fold and confirming $\\boxed{\\dfrac{7\\pi}{4}}$."
